- content_for :title, 'Love for Diversify'

%main#love
  %section.hero.is-medium
    .hero-body
      .container
        .box#hastag
          %h1.title.has-text-centered #diversify
          %h3.title.is-5.has-text-centered Hear what customers and businesses love about using Diversify


  %section.section
    .container
      %h1.title.has-text-centered Hear more from people like you

      .columns.is-multiline.is-vcentered
        .column.is-7
          .card
            .card-content
              .media
                .media-left
                  %figure.image.is-48x48
                    = image_tag 'avatar/small/daniel.jpg', class: 'is-rounded'
                .media-content
                  %p.title.is-4 Kalvin Howe
                  %p.subtitle.is-6 @kalvin
              .content
                I love using Diversify because of your TEAM! Diversify is the gold standard for team building and
                public projects. Cheers guys!
                = succeed '.' do
                  %a @diversify
                %a #diversify
                %a #diversifylove
                %a #teambuilding
                %time.is-block{datetime: "2019-10-29"} 11:09 AM - 29 Oct 2019
        .column.is-5
          .card
            .card-content
              .media
                .media-left
                  %figure.image.is-48x48
                    = image_tag 'avatar/small/veronika.jpg', class: 'is-rounded'
                .media-content
                  %p.title.is-4 Veronika Pace
                  %p.subtitle.is-6 @v.pace
              .content
                New
                %a @diversify
                is &#x1F525;
                %a #skilldiversity
                %a #culturaldiversity
                %time.is-block{datetime: "2019-1-7"} 13:05 PM - 7 Jan 2019
        .column.is-4
          .card
            .card-content
              .media
                .media-left
                  %figure.image.is-48x48
                    = image_tag 'avatar/small/kristy.png', class: 'is-rounded'
                .media-content
                  %p.title.is-4 Ade Reyes
                  %p.subtitle.is-6 @ade
              .content
                %a @diversify
                &#x1F92F; hands down is the best application I have used that has made my life 1000x easier.
                %a #taskallocation
                %a #skillrating
                %time.is-block{datetime: "2019-5-5"} 20:16 PM - 5 May 2019

        .column.is-8
          .card
            .card-content
              .media
                .media-left
                  %figure.image.is-48x48
                    = image_tag 'avatar/small/steve.jpg', class: 'is-rounded'
                .media-content
                  %p.title.is-4 Elvis Stout
                  %p.subtitle.is-6 @elvis
              .content
                Have never seen as open and as transparent a company as
                %a @diversify
                , loved browsing your website and looking for public projects to join. Definitely a torch bearer
                in employee satisfaction, loved your company dashboard.
                Learnt a lot today ! &#x2B50;&#x2B50;&#x2B50;&#x2B50;&#x2B50;
                %a #peerreview
                %a #public
                %a #projects
                %time.is-block{datetime: "2019-11-8"} 7:30 AM - 8 Nov 2019

  %section.hero.is-medium
    .hero-body
      .container.has-text-centered
        %h1.title More than 1000 businesses use Diversify.
        %h1.title Join us now.

        = link_to 'pricing', class: 'button is-primary is-large'  do
          Get Started for Free
